data.description: Presenting an exceptional opportunity at 905 Yardarm Lane, Annapolis. This well-crafted residence boasts enduring structural integrity, offering a solid foundation for personalized enhancements. Comprising 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, the home features a spacious living and dining area, seamlessly connected to a large kitchen.   The property also includes a one-car garage for added convenience. Enjoy outdoor living on the rear deck, perfect for relaxation or entertaining. Located within a highly regarded community, this property presents the ideal canvas for those seeking to create a bespoke living experience.  This is a short sale.  The mortgage servicer has been very quick to respond.
